The DisplayCurrentTime_Caller.c is the caller file in which the system call is called. Compile it using Makefile present in time_call/ directory.
The DisplayCurrentTime.c is the file in which the system call is defined. Compile it along with the kernel using Makefile present in kernel directory.
System call number and its entry point is defined in the file syscall_64.tbl.
Declaration of system call function is done in syscalls.h

